# Repository secrets for the gh-aw policy reviewer workflows.
# Configure these in GitHub repository settings:
# https://github.com/jbaruch/kotlin-tutor/settings/secrets/actions
#
# All three are required — the workflows fail-fast on activation if any is unset.

# OpenAI billing account for the Codex reviewer (`PR Policy Review (OpenAI)`).
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-proj-xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

# Anthropic billing account for the Claude Code reviewer (`PR Policy Review (Anthropic)`).
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

# Tessl registry token, used by the reviewer workflows' `tessl install` setup step.
# Generate at https://tessl.io/account/api-keys
TESSL_TOKEN=tessl_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
